text: Join us as we dive into how the AT Protocol is shaping BlueSky.
The AT Protocol introduces a decentralized social networking model, granting users full
ownership of their data and identity.
It separates personal data from platforms, enabling true data portability.
Unlike Blockchain and Mastodon, it employs a federated system with unique identifiers,
allowing for real control and scalability.
This innovative method is changing the dynamics of social media.
